strings.Value: "My spirit is stronger than any illness. By the light I shall cleanse myself of all filth, and with the new dawn I shall rise like the Sun."
"Merciful Sarenrae, I humbly beg you, hear my prayers and help me heal myself."
"You'd better resort to surer remedies. You're not looking so good."
"Buck up! Go pump some iron, or let's say... carry some sacks around. Helps me every time!"
"Tristian, you look so pale… but you know, it suits you well!"
"Just don't pray all night this time, and get some sleep. You need your strength. — If not for you, then think of the others."
"And I'd so hoped that I'd never again have to fall asleep listening to the sounds of prayers to Sarenrae..."
